There you go! Now, I'd like you to update `README.md` to fill in the "Extensibility" section just a bit more, documenting our plugin format (a function which accepts a configuration and returns `include` and `install` arrays to install dependent plugins and individual extensions, respectively). The update should be small, since we primarily want to just use `phantomaton-plugins` to manage details here.
